                        <h1 class="head1">Return & Refund Policy</h1>
                        <p>If you receive a product that does not match its description in our catalog, please notify us immediately. You may return the product for a refund or an exchange.</p>
                        
                        <h2 class="head2">Before You Return</h2>
                        <p>Please verify the product model and check the article before opening the package or breaking the seal. To qualify for a return, refund, or exchange, the content and packaging of the product must remain intact.</p>
                
                        <h2 class="head2">Refund Method and Timing</h2>
                        <p>We aim to reimburse you using the same method you used for payment, barring a few exceptions where an exchange might be preferable. Returns should be sent to our customer care center with all original packaging and accessories. We process returns within 3–5 business days after receipt and inspection. Refunds exclude delivery charges and may take up to 7 days to reflect in your account, depending on your bank’s processing time.</p>
                
                        <h2 class="head2">Returns Information</h2>
                        <p>Returned items must be in new, unboxed condition. Returns of damaged, unsanitary, dented, or scratched items may be denied.</p>
                        <p>Ensure all items are returned as received. Failure to do so may result in a denied return.</p>
                        <p>Reimbursements for returns without proof of purchase may be denied or limited.</p>
                
                        <h2 class="head2">Additional Information</h2>
                        <p>Read product descriptions carefully before making a purchase. Returns or exchanges due to 'change of mind' are not accepted if the product functions correctly.</p>
